OL,7,FThe "extreme" harms of two particular
OL,8,Fsubstances are taking the lives of men
OL,9,Facross parts of the LGBT+ community -
OL,10,Fa "crisis" very few seem to be
OL,11,Fcounting.
OL,13,FAn ITV News investigation has found a
OL,14,Fworrying lack of action into the
OL,15,Fextremely complex issue, with
OL,16,Frecommendations made to the previous
OL,17,Fgovernment not acted upon, which could
OL,18,Fhelp educate institutions to protect
OL,19,Fthousands of men who have sex with men
OL,20,Facross the country.
