OL,7,FOur investigation has found:
OL,9,FThe Metropolitan Police told ITV News
OL,10,Fthey fear 2024 will be the deadliest
OL,11,Fyet for chemsex deaths in London,
OL,12,Fafter figures for 2023 showed it
OL,13,Fclaimed three lives a month.
OL,15,FThe officer leading a unit dedicated
OL,16,Fto the issue told us the "harms
OL,17,Fpresent in this space are
OL,18,Fextreme...they're not going
OL,19,Faway...this is a national issue".
