OL,7,FOur investigation also collated data
OL,8,Facross multiple agencies and found the
OL,9,Fdamage to this particular subgroup is
OL,10,Fpractically invisible - we were given
OL,11,Fexclusive stats which showed almost a
OL,12,Fthird of all drug presentations at one
OL,13,Fof the countries busiest hospitals are
OL,14,Fdue to 'chemsex' related drugs - with
OL,15,Fone consultant calling on the NHS to
OL,16,Fdo better.
OL,18,FWhat is 'Chemsex'?
