OL,7,FIt's a term you've possibly never
OL,8,Fheard of - chemsex - it's essentially
OL,9,Fthe use of drugs to enhance sex. The
OL,10,Fpractice is more prevalent amongst
OL,11,Fgay, bi, and men who have sex with
OL,12,Fmen, but is not exclusive to this
OL,13,Fcohort.
OL,15,FOur investigation found that chemsex-
OL,16,Frelated drugs, namely GHB/GBL and
OL,17,FCrystal Meth, and which were once
OL,18,Fhidden behind closed doors, are by no
OL,19,Fmeans exclusively used for sex, with
OL,20,Fdevastating consequences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/47
