OL,7,FMore and more within the community are
OL,8,Fusing the potent and addictive drugs
OL,9,Frecreationally, likely by being in
OL,10,Fcloser proximity to the substances.
OL,11,FIt's a complicated link but hence why
OL,12,Fwe're using the term 'chemsex-related
OL,13,Fdrugs'.
OL,15,FWhat are chemsex-related drugs?
OL,17,FThe two illegal drugs which
OL,18,Fprofessionals are most concerned about
OL,19,Fare GHB/GBL and Crystal Meth.
