OL,7,FGHB/GBL is a Class B substance -
OL,8,Fcommonly referred to as 'G'. It's a
OL,9,Fcolourless liquid which can make the
OL,10,Fuser feel relaxed and aroused. But
OL,11,Fit's extremely easy to overdose on,
OL,12,Fjust a millilitre extra in a dose can
OL,13,Fbe fatal.
