OL,7,FI've been investigating this issue for
OL,8,Fseveral months, yet trying to convince
OL,9,Fpeople to talk openly about this topic
OL,10,Funderstandably proved challenging.
OL,11,FDuring this time I came across the
OL,12,Ffather of a 27-year-old who died after
OL,13,Foverdosing on chemsex-related drugs.
OL,15,F*Tahir's dad spoke to us on the
OL,16,Fcondition that we wouldn't name his
OL,17,Fson, as Tahir didn't want people to
OL,18,Fknow about the addiction that he faced
OL,19,Fduring his life.
