OL,7,FTahir's dad said ambulance reports
OL,8,Fsuggested that "the place had what
OL,9,Flooked like Class A substances at the
OL,10,Faddress. They found my son on the
OL,11,Ffloor, lying on his back with a towel
OL,12,Fon him."
OL,14,FTahir died at that address, he was
OL,15,Fjust 27-years-old. His body had lain
OL,16,Fundiscovered for 17 hours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/47
