OL,7,FHis dad said: "To spend his last hours
OL,8,Fwith no one around him to care for
OL,9,Fhim. Just left on the floor in a
OL,10,Fblanket. I feel like I let him down...
OL,11,FAs a parent, it's not what you're
OL,12,Fmeant to do. You're meant to protect
OL,13,Fthem. You're meant to be there for
OL,14,Fthem and we couldn't be there for him
OL,15,Fand feel a strong sense of failure."
OL,17,FTahir had Crystal Meth, GHB and
OL,18,FKetamine in his system when he died.
OL,19,FHis dad found out that Tahir had been
OL,20,Fengaging with these types of drugs on
OL,21,Fand off since he was a teenager.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/47
