OL,7,FTahir's dad went on to tell us: "When
OL,8,Fpeople talk about chemsex, it's
OL,9,Fsqualid and it's sordid the way it's
OL,10,Fdescribed and thought about, which for
OL,11,Fsomeone who's trying to guard their
OL,12,Freputation, is hardly going to
OL,13,Fencourage them to get some help."
OL,15,F"I don't think what Tahir was dealing
OL,16,Fwith and the ways that he was dealing
OL,17,Fwith them should have been a price so
OL,18,Fhigh he to had to pay... and that is a
OL,19,Fvery damning reflection of the world
OL,20,Fwe live in."
