OL,7,FNo codes, no data, no funding
OL,9,F"The LGBTQ community has been somewhat
OL,10,Fstigmatised in that these drugs are
OL,11,Fused predominantly by men who have sex
OL,12,Fwith men. But actually, as a society,
OL,13,Fwe're all prone to using a substance,
OL,14,Feven alcohol, to have sex with."
OL,16,FDr Naomi Fitzgerald, a sexual health
OL,17,Fconsultant at King's College Hospital
OL,18,Fin London, took a deeper dive into the
OL,19,Fstatistics at her hospital.
