OL,7,FShe told ITV News; "I've been working
OL,8,Fin this area for over 10 years and I
OL,9,Fhave seen the rise of chemsex happen
OL,10,Fover time. I think, particularly since
OL,11,Fthe pandemic, we've seen a real
OL,12,Fincrease in presentations secondary to
OL,13,Fthe harmful use of (GHB/GBL and
OL,14,FCrystal Meth).
