OL,7,FDr Naomi said: "I think it's a
OL,8,Freflection of the extent of the
OL,9,Fproblem, which perhaps for a long time
OL,10,Fhas slightly gone under the radar.
OL,11,FAnd, you know, perhaps the fact that
OL,12,Fit's been associated with the LGBTQ
OL,13,Fcommunity means that it's been
OL,14,Fslightly normalised and that's
OL,15,Fincorrect and not right."
OL,17,FWe can reveal almost a third of all
OL,18,Fdrug related presentations at King's
OL,19,FCollege Hospital are from GBL/GHB and
