OL,7,FBut Dr Fitzgerald took it upon herself
OL,8,Fto pull out this data, it's not
OL,9,Fsomething easily available, leaving
OL,10,Fhealthcare professionals and
OL,11,Fgovernment officials largely in the
OL,12,Fdark when it comes to this type of
OL,13,Fdrug usage.
OL,15,FThe NHS uses codes for drugs like
OL,16,Falcohol and some Class A substances.
OL,17,FIt means they can track data and put
OL,18,Fmoney towards various issues. That's
OL,19,Fnot the case for the likes of G or
