OL,15,Fthough, after leaving hospital they
OL,16,Fbegan taking Crystal Meth. They say:
OL,17,F"Crystal Meth is evil. It's a really
OL,18,Fdark place and its destructive
OL,19,Fcapability, not just on your life, but
OL,20,Fon your mind.
