OL,7,F"I am so sick of opening a social
OL,8,Fmedia app to learn that young gay men
OL,9,Fare dying. When it's not affecting
OL,10,Fstraight people...then it's sort of
OL,11,Fseen as (...) 'that is happening over
OL,12,Fthere.' Doesn't matter what
OL,13,Fcircumstances, chemsex or just, you
OL,14,Fknow, like me sitting there abusing it
OL,15,Fat home. More and more people are
OL,16,Fdying and nobody's talking about it."
